item.description:
Jet2 Holidays Meme Song (Instrumental) / aka Jess Glynne's "Hold My Hand"
[8 Second custom instrumental arrangement]



A 8 second custom instrumental arrangement of "Hold My Hand" by Jess Glynne, used in a Jet2 Holiday Ad (And now the mega viral meme).
This does not include Jess' vocals.
This ad was posted on Instagram by Jet2 and the track was cut by them too.
-
Note: This is a lossy track captured in a lossless .wav format to preserve quality!
